        <div class="msgSubject">Joint Bank Account?</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-11-21 20:48:17   | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-1290394096133973645" id="quote-1290394096133973645" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-1290394096133973645" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=28&amp;mid=1290394096133973645&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=1290394096133973645&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_1290394096133973645" onclick="followToggle('add','1290394096133973645')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
