      <div class="msgContentFrame">Me and my wife have both joint and separate accounts. The majority of the money are in joint accounts as those are where most of the spending occurs. Joint accounts are used for necessities like houses, cars, utilities and food. The personal accounts are used for things we want for ourselves. Easier this way, sucks if you make a big purchase and didn't notice one of the mortgage payments got pulled as well.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>call me for a good time ***-***-****</div></div>
