        <div class="msgUM"><a class="msgWhoName Sage" href="/users/Thumbelyna">Thumbelyna Quick Hands</a><div class="msgWhoTitle Sage">No Gag Reflex</div><div class="msgUMex"><a href="/journal.html?user=399238" class="icon-userjournal">View Journal</a></div></div><div class="msgAvatar"></div><div class="msgStar"><span class="bright">There is no 5th star.</span></div><div class="msgWhoNum">10,149 posts</div>
